	/**
	 * Returns the elevated visual treatment for the modern panel interface.
	 *
	 * this layer defines theme-mode surface tokens, header/sidebar/table
	 * chrome, mobile table card behavior, pagination styling, and focus/hover
	 * polish that sits on top of the structural frame CSS.
	 */
	private static function nextLevelUiCss(): string {
		return <<<'CSS'
